Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.55,0:00:12.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NI'm serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.85,0:00:14.47,Main,,0,0,0,,I wasn't going easy on her--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.56,0:00:16.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Everything felt\Nwrong that time!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.81,0:00:18.68,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO sniffs]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.77,0:00:20.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NI see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.56,0:00:26.32,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA cries]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.40,0:00:28.15,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU]\NWhy are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.24,0:00:33.24,Main,,0,0,0,,[crying continues]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.41,0:00:39.04,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU] Are you thinking\Nabout your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.12,0:00:40.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.34,0:00:46.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Or more specifically...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.46,0:00:47.30,Main,,0,0,0,,...about Ru?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.38,0:00:48.80,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA]\NHuh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.90,0:02:31.53,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL C pants]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.61,0:02:32.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.65,0:02:33.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, isn't it\Nthe creepiest thing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.03,0:02:35.70,Main,,0,0,0,,--you've ever heard?\N--[GIRL C] They're coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.78,0:02:36.66,Main,,0,0,0,,You see there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.74,0:02:38.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Look, what did I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.95,0:02:44.87,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOY A] Whoa, so it\Nreally is true, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.13,0:02:50.21,Main,,0,0,0,,--[GIRL D] Seriously?\N--[GIRL E] Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.29,0:02:51.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Akira's on the cover!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.75,0:02:53.17,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL F]\NWhat, where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.80,0:02:57.30,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL E] Ugh! Do those\Ntwo have, like, zero shame?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.38,0:02:58.72,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL F]\NI know!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.80,0:03:00.97,Main,,0,0,0,,They were walking side by\Nside like it was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.06,0:03:02.43,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL G]\NThe Kurebayashi twins?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.51,0:03:04.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that who you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.10,0:03:06.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL E] Yeah, the two who are\Nalways eating lunch together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.27,0:03:08.81,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL F]\NOn the rooftop, by themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.90,0:03:12.07,Main,,0,0,0,,But, come on, is it really true?\NThey are brother and sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.15,0:03:13.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe those two\Nare just really close.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.03,0:03:15.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL E]\NToo close if you ask me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.87,0:03:22.70,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI]\NWell, see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.79,0:03:23.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.62,0:03:25.04,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO (Y)]\NYup.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.38,0:03:34.80,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.51,0:03:43.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello, Ruko. How is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.72,0:03:47.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah? Um. Good;\Nshe's with Hitoe now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.48,0:03:49.90,Main,,0,0,0,,But they haven't been doing\NWIXOSS battles or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.98,0:03:52.02,Main,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.11,0:03:53.36,Main,,0,0,0,,But you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.44,0:03:55.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.32,0:03:57.24,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NUm. Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.32,0:03:59.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.36,0:04:00.95,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.03,0:04:04.33,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO (Y) sighs]\NNever mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.41,0:04:06.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Keep battling all you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.67,0:04:11.33,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NShe used to be an LRIG.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.42,0:04:12.67,Main,,0,0,0,,She knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.75,0:04:14.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, she knows\Nall about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.84,0:04:17.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Like just how different\Nyou are from the other girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.97,0:04:26.64,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NWhat is she trying to pull?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.73,0:04:27.98,Main,,0,0,0,,This can't be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.06,0:04:29.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.06,0:04:32.27,Main,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?\NYou're spacing out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.36,0:04:36.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps] I'm a bit worried\Nabout Ruko, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.69,0:04:37.32,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NYeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.40,0:04:38.90,Main,,0,0,0,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.99,0:04:41.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I got to thinking, and if what\Nyou said about Akira is true,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.95,0:04:45.33,Main,,0,0,0,,she probably will\Ngo after Ruko, and soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.75,0:04:52.50,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NDon't be ashamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.58,0:04:54.42,Main,,0,0,0,,I know you want to battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.13,0:05:00.84,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NI know how much you enjoyed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.93,0:05:04.76,Main,,0,0,0,,How your blood would flare\Nand your body would tingle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.85,0:05:07.01,Main,,0,0,0,,I could feel your passion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.48,0:05:10.69,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NIs it because Tama's gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.77,0:05:13.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Because I'm your LRIG now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.23,0:05:16.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Is it not fun anymore\Nbecause you're not with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.19,0:05:19.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that why you can't battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.36,0:05:21.74,Main,,0,0,0,,It makes no sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.82,0:05:24.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't you realize you're\Nthe most powerful Selector
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.41,0:05:27.66,Main,,0,0,0,,I've ever known? And I'm\Nthe most powerful LRIG?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.74,0:05:29.41,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a miracle that\Nwe've come together
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.50,0:05:31.87,Main,,0,0,0,,and you're letting\Nit all go to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.96,0:05:34.08,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL J]\NWhat? A new pack came out?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.17,0:05:35.58,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL I]\NYep! I just got it yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.67,0:05:37.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL J]\NAw, can you show it to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.17,0:05:38.42,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL I]\NSure!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.50,0:05:39.63,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA] That's why you're\Nstill carrying me around.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.71,0:05:42.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Isn't it? You hunger for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.26,0:05:43.43,Main,,0,0,0,,No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.51,0:05:45.10,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA] Using me to\Nfind Tama is just the lie
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.18,0:05:46.68,Main,,0,0,0,,you're telling yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.76,0:05:48.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop feeling guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.14,0:05:49.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Take advantage of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.56,0:05:50.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.52,0:05:51.77,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.85,0:05:53.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Take advantage of me--make\Nyourself feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.81,0:05:54.69,Main,,0,0,0,,You want this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.77,0:05:56.36,Main,,0,0,0,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.32,0:06:04.74,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NOf course it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.82,0:06:07.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Selectors fight to make\Ntheir wish come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.12,0:06:09.91,Main,,0,0,0,,And LRIGs fight to return\Nto the outside world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.99,0:06:12.71,Main,,0,0,0,,We've always taken\Nadvantage of each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.79,0:06:14.50,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NIt's not always like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.58,0:06:17.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Hanayo's still keeping Yuzuki's\Nwish for her, even now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.67,0:06:20.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA] She wants to live in\Nthe outside world, she has to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.30,0:06:21.67,Main,,0,0,0,,That's not my point!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.76,0:06:23.97,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA] You're saying\Nshe wants to do it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.05,0:06:26.68,Main,,0,0,0,,but how much do you really\Nknow about her anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.76,0:06:28.30,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.39,0:06:30.01,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.10,0:06:32.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Even about Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.48,0:06:33.81,Main,,0,0,0,,But that's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.89,0:06:36.10,Main,,0,0,0,,There's no need for you to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.19,0:06:39.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's just keep taking advantage\Nof one another, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.23,0:06:43.11,Main,,0,0,0,,And that way, you can keep\Nsavoring your battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.95,0:06:53.33,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] I'm telling you,\Nthat's all wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.41,0:06:57.21,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't care about winning\Nor wishes, or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.29,0:06:59.71,Main,,0,0,0,,It's because I was with Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.79,0:07:01.75,Main,,0,0,0,,I liked battling\Ntogether with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.84,0:07:02.92,Main,,0,0,0,,We were both a team!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.01,0:07:04.38,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.47,0:07:06.13,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not the battle\Npart I liked.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.22,0:07:09.14,Main,,0,0,0,,And it's not\Nthe battles I miss now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.22,0:07:11.22,Main,,0,0,0,,I liked being with Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.31,0:07:12.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.35,0:07:14.60,Main,,0,0,0,,You just can't admit\Nyou're like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.68,0:07:17.44,Main,,0,0,0,,You're only making excuses for\Nyour own desire to battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.52,0:07:20.19,Main,,0,0,0,,I just want Tama back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.19,0:07:22.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.27,0:07:23.69,Main,,0,0,0,,You promise you\Ndon't know anything
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.78,0:07:25.07,Main,,0,0,0,,about what happened to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.15,0:07:28.20,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you,\Nif you have even one clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.28,0:07:29.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll do anything\Nto get her back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.95,0:07:31.58,Main,,0,0,0,,And I don't care what it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.66,0:07:32.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you know where she is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:33.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Where she might be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.00,0:07:36.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.08,0:07:37.25,Main,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.33,0:07:40.17,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] You're not just\Nsaying that to trick me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.25,0:07:43.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe... she's with Mayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.09,0:07:44.17,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.25,0:07:46.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, what was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.47,0:07:48.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Never mind. It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.23,0:07:58.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU]\NWelcome back, Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.06,0:08:00.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.69,0:08:03.57,Main,,0,0,0,,It would seem\Nyou won your battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.65,0:08:04.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.82,0:08:06.44,Main,,0,0,0,,But I had to lie to Ru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.53,0:08:07.65,Main,,0,0,0,,You did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.74,0:08:10.74,Main,,0,0,0,,And I didn't even say\Ngoodbye, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.82,0:08:14.91,Main,,0,0,0,,So now, Ru is probably\Nawfully sad and crying, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.99,0:08:16.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, but Ru lied to you first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:18.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.16,0:08:19.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.42,0:08:28.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] So, hey, I can't wait\Nto go shopping with you, Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.30,0:08:30.55,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA]\NCan we eat dumplings?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.63,0:08:32.80,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] I was thinking\NI'd buy you some scrunchies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.89,0:08:34.60,Main,,0,0,0,,So you can match the rest of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.14,0:08:37.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA]\NRu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.60,0:08:39.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NI love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.31,0:08:40.98,Main,,0,0,0,,But now, after\Nwinning the battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.06,0:08:44.15,Main,,0,0,0,,you know... that Ru is a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.23,0:08:47.57,Main,,0,0,0,,She abandoned you, chose her\Nother friends instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.65,0:08:49.15,Main,,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.24,0:08:52.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru was trying to save Tama and\NYuzuki and Hitoe and everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.12,0:08:54.08,Main,,0,0,0,,That was gonna be her wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.99,0:08:58.87,Main,,0,0,0,,And yet, she's given up\Non all of you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.96,0:09:01.58,Main,,0,0,0,,No! It was my fault\Nthat it all went wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.67,0:09:03.92,Main,,0,0,0,,I ruined it all 'cause I was\Nscared about how lonely
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.00,0:09:06.71,Main,,0,0,0,,I would be if I lost her!\NIf I knew how she felt, then I--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.80,0:09:09.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NTama! Where did you go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.17,0:09:10.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.34,0:09:12.80,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NTama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.89,0:09:15.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.85,0:09:18.10,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA]\NI'm sorry, Ru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.18,0:09:20.35,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.43,0:09:21.81,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU]\NDo you want to see Ru?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.89,0:09:22.73,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA squeaks]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.81,0:09:24.81,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU]\NSee her and apologize?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.90,0:09:26.32,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA squeaks]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.40,0:09:27.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU]\NI take it you want to return
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.07,0:09:29.61,Main,,0,0,0,,to the outside world then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.69,0:09:31.49,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA]\NYes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.57,0:09:33.78,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU]\NIt's a frightening place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.87,0:09:36.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Both your emotions and your soul
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.08,0:09:39.12,Main,,0,0,0,,will become\Nhopelessly entangled.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.20,0:09:40.91,Main,,0,0,0,,You will be hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.00,0:09:43.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Everyone out there is a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.29,0:09:45.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Pain and sorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.38,0:09:47.46,Main,,0,0,0,,They're the only things\Nyou can count on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.54,0:09:48.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.63,0:09:50.05,Main,,0,0,0,,You can hear them...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.72,0:09:52.97,Main,,0,0,0,,The people...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.05,0:09:54.22,Main,,0,0,0,,They're crying...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.30,0:09:57.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but some are nice,\Nlike Ru and Grandma--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.81,0:09:58.68,Main,,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.76,0:09:59.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.72,0:10:00.89,Main,,0,0,0,,They're evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.98,0:10:01.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.06,0:10:03.73,Main,,0,0,0,,It's scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.81,0:10:04.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.69,0:10:07.15,Main,,0,0,0,,I-I don't wanna\Nleave, Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.23,0:10:11.11,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't ever live in that\Nhorrible world again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.19,0:10:13.36,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.45,0:10:16.95,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU]\NStay here, with me, forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.16,0:10:25.42,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU]\NAw, you're too strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.50,0:10:28.17,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.25,0:10:29.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Together...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.55,0:10:31.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Just like we were before...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.63,0:10:33.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Playing and laughing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.51,0:10:34.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.88,0:10:36.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.34,0:10:38.30,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA]\NI know her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.39,0:10:40.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I remember her voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.97,0:10:42.39,Main,,0,0,0,,She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.65,0:10:49.27,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA]\NMa... yu...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.36,0:10:51.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow, you remembered me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.45,0:11:05.33,Main,,0,0,0,,As for Ru, do you\Nstill want to see her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.41,0:11:06.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.54,0:11:07.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Really bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.88,0:11:11.21,Main,,0,0,0,,What if I said\NI won't forgive you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.30,0:11:14.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Then I'd say\NI still wanna see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.63,0:11:17.43,Main,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.51,0:11:19.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.47,0:11:21.51,Main,,0,0,0,,I suppose I'll let you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.23,0:11:28.27,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE]\NHold on a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.36,0:11:30.32,Main,,0,0,0,,It's like we said\Non the phone, Ruko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.40,0:11:32.19,Main,,0,0,0,,She's up to something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.27,0:11:33.36,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO (Y)]\NNever mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.44,0:11:36.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Keep battling all you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.57,0:11:37.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.57,0:11:39.24,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NWhat? You know something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.32,0:11:40.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.24,0:11:42.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps] Um, nevermind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.79,0:11:45.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Look, here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.12,0:11:46.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I was shocked!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.62,0:11:47.87,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.96,0:11:49.08,Main,,0,0,0,,You see now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.17,0:11:51.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Akira's looking for Selectors!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.01,0:11:58.59,Main,,0,0,0,,[whines]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.68,0:12:01.10,Main,,0,0,0,,She's also posting\Nrumors on the internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.18,0:12:02.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.85,0:12:04.89,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NWait, "mysterious LRIG cards
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.97,0:12:08.73,Main,,0,0,0,,that can grant wishes?"\NWhat could she be up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.81,0:12:11.15,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] She's not just\Ndrawing out Selectors,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.23,0:12:14.07,Main,,0,0,0,,she's also spreading the word\Nabout them to everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.15,0:12:16.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NGot more fans than ever, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.28,0:12:18.99,Main,,0,0,0,,That's already been\Nretweeted over 5,000 times.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.07,0:12:20.20,Main,,0,0,0,,At this rate, she'll--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.28,0:12:21.87,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL K] The WIXOSS\NLRIG cards can speak,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.95,0:12:23.78,Main,,0,0,0,,and then you can get\Nyour wish to come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.87,0:12:26.08,Main,,0,0,0,,That sounds familiar.\NIs it from the novel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.16,0:12:28.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL M]\NEven if it is, it's stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.08,0:12:29.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.46,0:12:30.88,Main,,0,0,0,,No one's ever gonna believe\Na crazy rumor like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.96,0:12:33.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL L] Well, Akira was talking\Nabout it on the internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.29,0:12:34.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL M]\NYeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.29,0:12:35.75,Main,,0,0,0,,See, that's what\NI'm worried about.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.84,0:12:36.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you hear them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.05,0:12:38.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Look, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.76,0:12:40.97,Main,,0,0,0,,One of them even said\Nno one'll ever believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.05,0:12:42.35,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NWe can't be so sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.43,0:12:44.05,Main,,0,0,0,,We've gotta do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.14,0:12:45.47,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NOkay, but what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.56,0:12:47.77,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know, but we\Ncan't just leave this be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.85,0:12:49.77,Main,,0,0,0,,The first thing we should do\Nis try to figure out
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.85,0:12:52.90,Main,,0,0,0,,why Akira is doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.98,0:12:54.32,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE]\NYou have to admit,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.40,0:12:56.40,Main,,0,0,0,,she is... really pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.48,0:12:57.65,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NHitoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.74,0:12:59.53,Main,,0,0,0,,We need to be planning,\Nnot praising her looks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.61,0:13:02.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh! Right! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.82,0:13:07.00,Main,,0,0,0,,For some reason, she does look\Na lot nicer than before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.08,0:13:09.00,Main,,0,0,0,,It even seems like\Nher scar is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.08,0:13:11.58,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] I'm sure she just\Ncovered it with makeup.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.67,0:13:12.67,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE]\NYou think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.75,0:13:13.96,Main,,0,0,0,,I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.04,0:13:14.88,Main,,0,0,0,,It's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.96,0:13:15.59,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.67,0:13:16.71,Main,,0,0,0,,You what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.80,0:13:18.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Akira's scar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.38,0:13:20.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, I... saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.26,0:13:22.51,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NYou met with her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.59,0:13:25.10,Main,,0,0,0,,I had a bad feeling\Nshe'd go after you, Ruko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.18,0:13:27.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.31,0:13:28.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.14,0:13:29.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.73,0:13:31.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.14,0:13:33.61,Main,,0,0,0,,I-I had a battle with Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.69,0:13:35.73,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI, HITOE gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.69,0:13:41.11,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA]\NUrith...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.20,0:13:42.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Urith...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.28,0:13:46.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Urith... Urith...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.28,0:13:47.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Urith...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.58,0:13:51.33,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH (I)]\NSo, did you beat Ruko or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.41,0:13:53.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Some guy interrupted the battle,\Nso we weren't able to finish,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.04,0:13:56.88,Main,,0,0,0,,but up until that point,\NI was totally kicking her ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.96,0:13:58.75,Main,,0,0,0,,But don't worry,\Nnext time I play that snot,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.84,0:14:01.26,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll squash her like\Na bug, and then--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.34,0:14:03.05,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH (I)]\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.13,0:14:05.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't tell you how much\NI appreciate you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.14,0:14:06.22,Main,,0,0,0,,doing that for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.30,0:14:09.72,Main,,0,0,0,,No, Urith. I appreciate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.81,0:14:12.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks to your love, I can show\Nmy face to everyone again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.89,0:14:14.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.27,0:14:15.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.69,0:14:18.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[grunts] Hey! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.90,0:14:20.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Then why do you hide it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.57,0:14:25.16,Main,,0,0,0,,If you do appreciate\Nme like you say,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.24,0:14:27.03,Main,,0,0,0,,then show all of it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.12,0:14:29.66,Main,,0,0,0,,That means all the\Nunsightly things, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.74,0:14:33.46,Main,,0,0,0,,The splattered, rotten, filthy\Nparts that bring you shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.54,0:14:36.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Or is it... that you\Ncan't show them to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.67,0:14:37.92,Main,,0,0,0,,I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.00,0:14:40.59,Main,,0,0,0,,I can and I will, I swear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.67,0:14:42.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA sobs]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.92,0:14:45.13,Main,,0,0,0,,You've got it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.22,0:14:46.93,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not hiding it from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.01,0:14:48.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll show you anything you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.93,0:14:50.89,Main,,0,0,0,,And I'll do anything\Nyou ask me to!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.97,0:14:53.10,Main,,0,0,0,,I'd kill Ruko to make you happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.18,0:14:54.35,Main,,0,0,0,,So please...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.44,0:14:55.39,Main,,0,0,0,,...I'm begging you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.48,0:14:56.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Urith...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.44,0:14:58.19,Main,,0,0,0,,...love me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.27,0:15:03.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Turn me from Aki-lucky...\Ninto Aki-lovely...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.28,0:15:04.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Please...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.61,0:15:06.41,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA sobs]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.49,0:15:07.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE]\NSo your battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.66,0:15:09.66,Main,,0,0,0,,it got interrupted?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.74,0:15:11.58,Main,,0,0,0,,[sighs] You're lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.66,0:15:12.87,Main,,0,0,0,,No, she's stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.95,0:15:15.62,Main,,0,0,0,,What possessed you\Nto do such a thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.71,0:15:19.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I just had a bad feeling\Nthat if I said no to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.25,0:15:20.25,Main,,0,0,0,,there was a chance\Nthat something
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.34,0:15:21.84,Main,,0,0,0,,even worse might happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.92,0:15:23.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Save the lame excuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.30,0:15:25.38,Main,,0,0,0,,You just wanted to\Nbattle her, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.47,0:15:26.55,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NAh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.63,0:15:27.72,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] Now you're\Njumping to conclusions!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:30.30,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NAm I? Are you carrying Iona?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.39,0:15:32.93,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]\NUh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.89,0:15:38.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.73,0:15:39.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.81,0:15:42.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Is it because you\Nwant to find Tama?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.11,0:15:43.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.32,0:15:44.32,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] But if you\Nlose Selector battles,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.40,0:15:46.32,Main,,0,0,0,,you might not get that chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.41,0:15:49.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NHow petty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.99,0:15:51.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Your grandma would be crushed\Nif something happened to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.74,0:15:52.62,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NRidiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.70,0:15:54.08,Main,,0,0,0,,I know that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.16,0:15:55.58,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NShe's not like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.66,0:15:58.63,Main,,0,0,0,,We said we'd work\Ntogether to find Tama, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.29,0:16:03.92,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA] Ruko only truly enjoys\Nlife when she's in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.00,0:16:05.63,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] And that you\Ndidn't have to shoulder
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.72,0:16:07.47,Main,,0,0,0,,this responsibility on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.55,0:16:08.84,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NShe's like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.93,0:16:10.39,Main,,0,0,0,,We should be working together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.47,0:16:12.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Fighting together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.26,0:16:15.18,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NIt's because I was with Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.27,0:16:16.77,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NThey're misleading her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.85,0:16:19.52,Main,,0,0,0,,They're the reason\NRuko is like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.44,0:16:24.15,Main,,0,0,0,,It's okay, we understand.\NWe feel the same way you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.23,0:16:25.44,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.53,0:16:28.70,Main,,0,0,0,,You know that special\Nway you feel about Tama?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.78,0:16:32.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, Hitoe and I, we feel\Nthe same way about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.70,0:16:34.24,Main,,0,0,0,,We do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.33,0:16:36.58,Main,,0,0,0,,And if you disappeared\Nthe same way Tama did,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.66,0:16:38.96,Main,,0,0,0,,we'd be just as\Nupset as you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.04,0:16:40.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.75,0:16:42.17,Main,,0,0,0,,You know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.25,0:16:45.30,Main,,0,0,0,,When you won that battle with\NIona, I got really scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.38,0:16:49.17,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought at first that we\Nmight not ever see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.26,0:16:51.09,Main,,0,0,0,,And I was really worried\Nthat you were going to be
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.18,0:16:52.85,Main,,0,0,0,,transformed into an LRIG.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.93,0:16:56.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Or, in the worst case, you\Nmight even disappear forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.02,0:16:58.64,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NHitoe...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.73,0:17:01.27,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] We know you\Nwanted to sacrifice yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.35,0:17:03.61,Main,,0,0,0,,for Tama and for all the\Nother Selectors and LRIGs
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.69,0:17:05.11,Main,,0,0,0,,who are suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.19,0:17:08.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but Hitoe, you would do\Nthe same thing for Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.86,0:17:11.78,Main,,0,0,0,,I would've done anything,\Nno matter what happened to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.87,0:17:13.07,Main,,0,0,0,,because we're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.16,0:17:14.70,Main,,0,0,0,,But that's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.78,0:17:16.41,Main,,0,0,0,,That's not the way\Nfriendship works!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.49,0:17:18.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.08,0:17:20.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I finally got it when I thought\Nyou were gonna disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.96,0:17:22.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Just think.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.54,0:17:25.00,Main,,0,0,0,,If you were gone,\NI wouldn't be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.09,0:17:27.21,Main,,0,0,0,,What if you had\Nsacrificed yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.30,0:17:29.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if it did go\Nlike you planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.84,0:17:31.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe I could have\Nhad a normal life,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.38,0:17:32.97,Main,,0,0,0,,been able to\Ntalk to Yuzuki,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.05,0:17:34.55,Main,,0,0,0,,possibly even make\Nsome other friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.64,0:17:37.18,Main,,0,0,0,,But still, don't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.27,0:17:39.64,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE sobs]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.73,0:17:41.69,Main,,0,0,0,,If you weren't there to\Nshare those things with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.77,0:17:45.07,Main,,0,0,0,,well then, it wouldn't\Nbe any fun at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.94,0:17:48.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.86,0:17:49.99,Main,,0,0,0,,The thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.07,0:17:53.07,Main,,0,0,0,,...we talked after your battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.16,0:17:55.95,Main,,0,0,0,,We talked about sacrificing\Nourselves for others,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.03,0:17:57.87,Main,,0,0,0,,and agreed to stop\Ndoing stuff like that
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.95,0:18:01.16,Main,,0,0,0,,'cause it's not necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.25,0:18:03.08,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll always be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.17,0:18:05.71,Main,,0,0,0,,So if we suffer,\Nat least we're not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.79,0:18:08.46,Main,,0,0,0,,If we're sad, we'll\Nstill have each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.55,0:18:11.51,Main,,0,0,0,,So this is what we'll do,\Nfor as long as we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.59,0:18:13.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.43,0:18:14.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.60,0:18:20.31,Main,,0,0,0,,I was... just trying\Nto get Tama back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.39,0:18:23.27,Main,,0,0,0,,I had no idea how much\NI upset you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.35,0:18:25.11,Main,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.19,0:18:27.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.11,0:18:28.69,Main,,0,0,0,,I mean that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.78,0:18:31.57,Main,,0,0,0,,And... I won't\Ndo it again, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.65,0:18:34.28,Main,,0,0,0,,No more battles\Non my own, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.36,0:18:35.03,Main,,0,0,0,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.12,0:18:37.20,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.28,0:18:38.33,Main,,0,0,0,,We understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.41,0:18:40.29,Main,,0,0,0,,It's all for Tama, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.37,0:18:42.83,Main,,0,0,0,,And to prevent anyone else from\Ngoing through all the suffering
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.91,0:18:44.16,Main,,0,0,0,,we've gone through.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.25,0:18:46.75,Main,,0,0,0,,So, if you have to battle,\Nto stand up for them...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.84,0:18:48.04,Main,,0,0,0,,...we won't stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.13,0:18:50.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Just be sure you\Ntell us first, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.67,0:18:54.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you both, so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.93,0:19:01.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[ALL giggle]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.86,0:19:14.70,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI]\NYuzuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.78,0:19:17.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.24,0:19:19.24,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI]\NMm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.25,0:19:26.62,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Mm, I could eat,\Nlike, five of these!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.71,0:19:29.04,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess all of that crying\Nmade us hungry, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.13,0:19:30.50,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.59,0:19:32.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NWhat're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.09,0:19:35.05,Main,,0,0,0,,You do realize we just\Nleft a restaurant, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.13,0:19:37.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.47,0:19:38.89,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NWhat're you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.97,0:19:41.85,Main,,0,0,0,,We were making a sobbing scene;\Nbest to get out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.93,0:19:43.02,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NRuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.10,0:19:45.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Why can't you see\Nyou're not one of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.77,0:19:48.56,Main,,0,0,0,,And, y'know, snack away,\Nbecause it's not like I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.65,0:19:50.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Can you smell stuff at least?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.44,0:19:53.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA] I became an LRIG\Njust for you, Ruko.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.48,0:19:56.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, come to think of it,\Ndo LRIGs ever get hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.28,0:19:57.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, no, we don't actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.07,0:19:59.24,Main,,0,0,0,,But thanks for asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.32,0:20:01.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA] To become one\Nwith you in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.08,0:20:03.08,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.16,0:20:05.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NDo not let me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.00,0:20:11.21,Main,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.29,0:20:12.46,Main,,0,0,0,,You guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.55,0:20:14.13,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sensing another LRIG!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.21,0:20:15.13,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.21,0:20:16.26,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NThere's a Selector nearby!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.34,0:20:18.51,Main,,0,0,0,,There is?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.59,0:20:20.01,Main,,0,0,0,,That way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.72,0:20:26.06,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NIt's her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.44,0:20:31.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE, RUKO gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.44,0:20:35.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.82,0:20:37.44,Main,,0,0,0,,...Urith!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.53,0:20:38.36,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH (I)]\NHmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.45,0:20:40.49,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NHmph. Urith.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.57,0:20:42.28,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI gasps]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.37,0:20:43.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Chiyori?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.70,0:20:45.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Yay! I knew my Super\NSelector Sense was tingling!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.99,0:20:47.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, well!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.16,0:20:49.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Looks like the whole gang\Nshowed up today!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.08,0:20:50.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but why oh why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.42,0:20:52.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait! I bet\Nit's destiny, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.59,0:20:55.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Why else would we beautiful\NSelectors of love and courage
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.09,0:20:56.34,Main,,0,0,0,,be brought together, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.42,0:20:58.47,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA] Did you just call\Nyourself "beautiful?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.55,0:21:01.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, we meet again,\NMiss Pain-in-the-ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.47,0:21:02.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.60,0:21:04.47,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you doing with Chiyori?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.56,0:21:05.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Hah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.22,0:21:07.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Look...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.06,0:21:10.39,Main,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.48,0:21:11.94,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH (I)]\NWell then, Chiyori.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.02,0:21:13.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you ready to start?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.44,0:21:16.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, let's do it!\NIt's battle time, ladies!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.44,0:21:19.86,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.49,0:21:21.36,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI, URITH (I)]\NOpen!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.45,0:21:22.87,Main,,0,0,0,,No, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.83,0:21:26.24,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.33,0:21:27.75,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.79,0:21:31.92,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOTH grunt]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.34,0:21:43.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.09,0:21:44.51,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.64,0:21:52.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Wha--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.81,0:21:54.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.62,0:23:34.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NOh yeah! Hoo-yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.79,0:23:36.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH (I)]\NLucky us--we get to go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.96,0:23:37.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Now Grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.96,0:23:38.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NWe're like rivals, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.79,0:23:39.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH (I)]\NWish Crisis!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.96,0:23:42.92,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NChorizo De Ibéricoña The Second!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.01,0:23:44.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Wa-pa-pow!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.42,0:23:47.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Next time:\N"Those Wild Delusions."
